 it should). peace - [[User:קיפודנחש|קיפודנחש (aka kipod)]] ([[User talk:קיפודנחש|talk]]) 14:50, 30 May 2013 (UTC)  {{od}} Still not working guys. [[User:GiantSnowman|Giant]][[User talk:GiantSnowman|Snowman]] 21:39, 30 May 2013 (UTC) :you did not answer my question, so here goes:  can you try to see if you have the same problem with a different browser? peace - [[User:קיפודנחש|קיפודנחש (aka kipod)]] ([[User talk:קיפודנחש|talk]]) 22:48, 30 May 2013 (UTC) ::It's fine on an older version of the same browser (IE) at a different computer, and it's fine on my iPad - but not on IE10. [[User:GiantSnowman|Giant]][[User talk:GiantSnowman|Snowman]] 09:44, 31 May 2013 (UTC) :::can you do me a favor? from your "watchlist" page, hit F12 and select "console" (it will probably ask you to refresh the page at this point - do it), and post here if you see any errors (typically appear in red) on the console? thanks, peace - [[User:קיפודנחש|קיפודנחש (aka kipod)]] ([[User talk:קיפודנחש|talk]]) 13:49, 31 May 2013 (UTC)  {{od}} Guys, I think it was because I was in 'compatibility' mode. Seems to be fixed now... [[User:GiantSnowman|Giant]][[User talk:GiantSnowman|Snowman]] 18:39, 31 May 2013 (UTC)  == User contributions oddity ==  Not sure if there is something there that needs fixing, but I thought it was pretty strange. See the feedback summary by  [[Special:Contributions/176.42.16.120|176.42.16.120]] at [[Wikipedia:Automatic edit summaries]]. I don't think it's supposed to do that... --[[User:Bongwarrior|Bongwarrior]] ([[User talk:Bongwarrior|talk]]) 17:58, 30 May 2013 (UTC) :Looks like the parser is evaluating the template...[[User:Okeyes (WMF)|Oliver]], if you're out there, since [[WP:AFT|AFT]] is your baby, take a look? '''[[User:Theopolisme|<span style="color:#232323;">Theopolisme</span>]] <span style="color:#4F4F4F;">([[User talk:Theopolisme|<span style="color:#4F4F4F;">talk</span>]])</span>''' 18:01, 30 May 2013 (UTC) ::It's...oh lord. Escaping exists for a reason :/. Okay, I'll le